#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft.ifft:1 of
msgid "Compute the one-dimensional inverse discrete Fourier Transform."
msgstr "计算一维离散傅里叶逆变换。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft.ifft:3 of
msgid ""
"This function computes the inverse of the one-dimensional *n*-point "
"discrete Fourier transform computed by `fft`.  In other words, "
"``ifft(fft(a)) == a`` to within numerical accuracy. For a general "
"description of the algorithm and definitions, see `mt.fft`."
msgstr ""
"此函数计算由 `fft` 计算的一维 *n* 点离散傅里叶变换的逆变换。换句话说，``"
"ifft(fft(a)) == a`` 在数值精度范围内成立。有关算法和定义的一般描述，请"
"参见 `mt.fft`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft.ifft:9 of
msgid "The input should be ordered in the same way as is returned by `fft`, i.e.,"
msgstr "输入应按照 `fft` 返回的顺序排列，即："

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft.ifft:12 of
msgid "``a[0]`` should contain the zero frequency term,"
msgstr "``a[0]`` 应包含零频率项，"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft.ifft:13 of
msgid "``a[1:n//2]`` should contain the positive-frequency terms,"
msgstr "``a[1:n//2]`` 应包含正频率项，"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft.ifft:14 of
msgid ""
"``a[n//2 + 1:]`` should contain the negative-frequency terms, in "
"increasing order starting from the most negative frequency."
msgstr "``a[n//2 + 1:]`` 应包含负频率项，按从最负频率开始递增的顺序排列。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft.ifft:17 of
msgid ""
"For an even number of input points, ``A[n//2]`` represents the sum of the"
" values at the positive and negative Nyquist frequencies, as the two are "
"aliased together. See `numpy.fft` for details."
msgstr ""
"对于偶数个输入点，``A[n//2]`` 表示正负奈奎斯特频率处的值之和，因为这两个"
"频率混叠在一起。详见 `numpy.fft`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft.ifft of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft.ifft:21 of
msgid "Input tensor, can be complex."
msgstr "输入张量，可以是复数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft.ifft:23 of
msgid ""
"Length of the transformed axis of the output. If `n` is smaller than the "
"length of the input, the input is cropped. If it is larger, the input is "
"padded with zeros.  If `n` is not given, the length of the input along "
"the axis specified by `axis` is used. See notes about padding issues."
msgstr ""
"输出变换轴的长度。如果 `n` 小于输入长度，则输入会被裁剪；如果大于输入长度"
"，则输入会被补零。如果未指定 `n`，则使用沿 `axis` 指定轴的输入长度。有关"
"填充问题，请参见说明。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft.ifft:29 of
msgid ""
"Axis over which to compute the inverse DFT.  If not given, the last axis "
"is used."
msgstr "用于计算逆离散傅里叶变换的轴。如果未指定，则使用最后一个轴。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft.ifft:32 of
msgid "Normalization mode (see `numpy.fft`). Default is None."
msgstr "归一化模式（参见 `numpy.fft`）。默认为 None。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft.ifft of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft.ifft:35 of
msgid ""
"**out** -- The truncated or zero-padded input, transformed along the axis"
" indicated by `axis`, or the last one if `axis` is not specified."
msgstr ""
"**out** -- 经过截断或补零的输入，沿 `axis` 指定的轴进行变换；如果未指定 `"
"axis`，则沿最后一个轴变换。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft.ifft of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft.ifft of
msgid "抛出"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft.ifft:39 of
msgid "If `axes` is larger than the last axis of `a`."
msgstr "如果 `axes` 大于 `a` 的最后一个轴。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft.ifft:43 of
msgid ":py:obj:`mt.fft`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft.ifft:44 of
msgid "An introduction, with definitions and general explanations."
msgstr "介绍，包含定义和一般性说明。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft.ifft:46 of
msgid ":py:obj:`fft`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft.ifft:47 of
msgid "The one-dimensional (forward) FFT, of which `ifft` is the inverse"
msgstr "一维（正向）快速傅里叶变换，`ifft` 是其逆变换"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft.ifft:49 of
msgid ":py:obj:`ifft2`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft.ifft:50 of
msgid "The two-dimensional inverse FFT."
msgstr "二维逆快速傅里叶变换。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft.ifft:52 of
msgid ":py:obj:`ifftn`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft.ifft:53 of
msgid "The n-dimensional inverse FFT."
msgstr "n维逆快速傅里叶变换。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft.ifft:56 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft.ifft:57 of
msgid ""
"If the input parameter `n` is larger than the size of the input, the "
"input is padded by appending zeros at the end.  Even though this is the "
"common approach, it might lead to surprising results.  If a different "
"padding is desired, it must be performed before calling `ifft`."
msgstr ""
"如果输入参数 `n` 大于输入大小，则在输入末尾补零。虽然这是常见的做法，但"
"可能导致令人意外的结果。如果需要不同的填充方式，必须在调用 `ifft` 之前"
"完成。"

